# Query Analyzer Service — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

The **Layer 5 Structured Query Analyzer** for HelioX RAG 3.0, implementing FR-3.1 through FR-3.8. The service takes a raw user query and produces a locked **Structured Query Object (SQO)** for downstream retrieval.

## Files Created

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [__init__.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/__init__.py) | Package init |
| [config.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/config.py) | Service settings (confidence threshold, retries, timeout) |
| [schemas.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/schemas.py) | SQO schema, [QueryIntent](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/schemas.py#21-28) enum, constraints, API DTOs |
| [intent_classifier.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/intent_classifier.py) | Rule-based 4-intent classifier (fact/comparison/synthesis/compliance) |
| [entity_extractor.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/entity_extractor.py) | Query-focused NER (proper nouns, acronyms, regulations, dates) |
| [constraint_extractor.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/constraint_extractor.py) | Temporal, geographic, regulatory, scope extraction |
| [decomposer.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/decomposer.py) | LLM-based fact/reasoning decomposition with retry |
| [validator.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/validator.py) | Ambiguity detection, constraint defaults, entity grounding, SQO lock |
| [analyzer.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/analyzer.py) | Main orchestrator coordinating all 5 stages |
| [routes.py](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/routes.py) | `POST /v1/query/analyze` FastAPI endpoint |

## SQO Schema

```json
{
  "query_id": "uuid",
  "original_query": "string",
  "intent": "fact | comparison | synthesis | compliance",
  "entities": ["entity_a", "entity_b"],
  "constraints": {
    "temporal": {"after": "2024-01-01", "before": null},
    "geographic": ["EU"],
    "regulatory": ["GDPR"],
    "scope": "section-level"
  },
  "fact_components": ["sub-question-1", "sub-question-2"],
  "reasoning_components": ["compare X vs Y on dimension Z"],
  "decomposition_confidence": 0.87,
  "ambiguity_warnings": [],
  "ungrounded_entities": [],
  "locked": true
}
```

## API Endpoint

**`POST /v1/query/analyze`** — Input: `{query, session_context?}` → Output: `{sqo, warnings[], analysis_time_ms}`

## Validation Rules

| Rule | FR | Behavior |
|------|-----|----------|
| Ambiguity detection | FR-3.5 | Warns on no entities, short queries, or missing constraints |
| Missing constraint injection | FR-3.5 | Defaults scope to `section-level` |
| Entity grounding | FR-3.6 | Stub: marks entities as ungrounded (requires corpus) |
| Decomposition confidence | FR-3.7 | Retries once if confidence < 0.65 |
| SQO lock | FR-3.8 | Sets `locked=true` — immutable downstream |

